Letâ€™s learn for loop in java.

for loop is used to iterate a block of statements multiple times. Use for loop if you know the number of iteration is fixed.

Syntax

for(initialization; condition; increment/decrement)
{
   statement(s).....
}

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

java for loop example

public class ForLoop
{
   public static void main(String[] args)
   {
      for(int x = 1; x <= 5; x++)
      {
         System.out.println(x);
      }
   }
}


Output:

1
2
3
4
5
